name: Wholesome Gift
description: A gift box that spawns a wholesome buff! Consumed when used.

name: Breeder Trait
description: Apply this trait to a fish! Consumed when used. Creates another fish of the same specie every 30 minutes.

name: King Trait
description: Apply this trait to a fish! Consumed when used. Generates a coin regularly that is worth 0.1% of the Income Multiplier upgrade cost.

name: Giant Trait
description: Apply this trait to a fish! Consumed when used. Makes the fish huge and worth 25x.

name: Big Baby Trait
description: Apply this trait to a fish! Consumed when used. Makes even grown up fish appear in their baby form. Earning per second is doubled.

name: Gold Fever Pal Trait
description: Apply this trait to a fish! Consumed when used. Earning per second is multiplied 5x.

name: Unicorn Trait
description: Apply this trait to a fish! Consumed when used. Earning per second is multiplied 10x, and generates a coin regularly that is worth 0.2% of the Income Multiplier upgrade cost.

name: Gatherer Trait
description: Apply this trait to a fish! Consumed when used. A fish with this trait will automatically collects any wholesome buffs touched.

name: Fez Trait
description: Apply this trait to a fish! Consumed when used. Generates a gem regularly that is worth 0.15% of the Income Multiplier upgrade cost.
